---
title: Cosy Double Cumberland Sausage Traybake with Sticky Glazed Apples, Roasted Carrots and Cheesy Wedges
description: In this traybake, we're roasting sausages, potato wedges, carrots and apples on trays in the oven. Just add the finishing touches by sprinkling cheese over the wedges and apple and sage jelly over the apples.
